---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Dental Implants" 
  category="Advanced Treatments"
  description="Permanent tooth replacement with titanium implants that look, feel, and function like natural teeth."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811971618-4486d14f3f99?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">The Gold Standard in Tooth Replacement</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Dental implants are titanium posts that replace tooth roots, providing a strong foundation for 
        permanent replacement teeth. They're the closest you can get to natural teeth in both appearance 
        and function.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Why Choose Dental Implants?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Natural Look & Feel</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Implants look and function exactly like your natural teeth
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Lifetime Solution</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          With proper care, implants can last a lifetime
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Preserve Bone</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Stimulates bone growth and prevents deterioration
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Implant Process
    </h2>

    <div class="relative mb-12">
      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-900 to-accent-300"></div>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold z-10">
            1
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Consultation & Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Comprehensive exam with X-rays and 3D imaging to assess bone density and plan optimal implant placement.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-900 font-medium">Timeline: Same day</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold z-10">
            2
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Implant Placement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Titanium post is surgically placed into the jawbone. Procedure is done under local anesthetic for comfort.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-900 font-medium">Timeline: 1-2 hours</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold z-10">
            3
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Osseointegration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Implant fuses with jawbone creating a strong, permanent foundation. Temporary tooth provided during healing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-900 font-medium">Timeline: 3-6 months</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-900 text-xl font-bold z-10">
            4
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Crown Placement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Custom-made crown is attached to the implant, perfectly matching your natural teeth in color and shape.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-900 font-medium">Timeline: 2 appointments</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Types of Implant Solutions
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Single Tooth Implant</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Replace a single missing tooth without affecting neighboring teeth. The most common and 
          straightforward implant procedure.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>No damage to adjacent teeth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Easy to clean and maintain</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Multiple Implants</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Replace several missing teeth with individual implants or implant-supported bridges for 
          optimal function and aesthetics.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Restore full chewing function</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Prevent shifting of remaining teeth</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">All-on-4Â® Implants</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Full arch restoration using just four strategically placed implants. Perfect for patients 
          missing all upper or lower teeth.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>New teeth in one day possible</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>No need for bone grafting</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Implant-Supported Dentures</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Secure your dentures with implants for improved stability and confidence. No more slipping 
          or clicking when you eat or speak.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Removable for easy cleaning</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>More affordable than fixed options</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Invest in Your Smile's Future
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Dental implants are a lifetime investment in your oral health, confidence, and quality of life. 
        Schedule a consultation to explore your implant options.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Implant Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/extractions" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Tooth Extractions</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Prepare for implant placement</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Crowns & Bridges</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Alternative restoration options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/dentures" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dentures</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Removable tooth replacement</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Am I a candidate for dental implants?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most adults with good general health and adequate jawbone density are candidates for implants. 
        Even if you've been told you don't have enough bone, procedures like bone grafting can often 
        make implants possible. We'll evaluate your specific situation during a consultation.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long do dental implants last?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        With proper care and regular dental visits, dental implants can last a lifetime. The crown 
        attached to the implant may need replacement after 10-15 years due to normal wear, but the 
        implant itself is designed to be permanent.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Is the implant procedure painful?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most patients report that implant placement is more comfortable than they expected. We use 
        local anesthetic during the procedure, and many patients manage post-operative discomfort 
        with over-the-counter pain medication. IV sedation is available for anxious patients.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How much do dental implants cost?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        While implants have a higher initial cost than other tooth replacement options, they're often 
        more economical in the long run because they can last a lifetime. We offer flexible payment 
        plans and work with your insurance to maximize benefits. Schedule a consultation for a personalized quote.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>